  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Brand Manager (B2B / Distributor Marketing)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>hands-on Assistant Brand Manager</strong> to support brand and marketing initiatives with a <strong>strong focus on B2B and distributor collaboration</strong>. This role works closely with internal sales teams and external distributors to support brand execution, trade initiatives, and go-to-market activities.</p><p>The ideal candidate has experience supporting <strong>distributor-facing marketing</strong>, trade campaigns, and commercial alignment, and is comfortable working in a fast-paced, cross-functional environment.</p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Support brand and marketing initiatives across <strong>B2B and distributor channels</strong></p></li><li><p>Liaise directly with <strong>distributors and channel partners</strong> to support marketing execution and campaigns</p></li><li><p>Assist in preparing <strong>sell-in decks, trade presentations, and distributor toolkits</strong></p></li><li><p>Coordinate brand activations, promotions, and launches with sales and distributors</p></li><li><p>Support <strong>joint business planning (JBP)</strong>, promotional calendars, and campaign tracking</p></li><li><p>Work closely with Sales, Trade Marketing, and Operations teams to ensure smooth execution</p></li><li><p>Track campaign performance, distributor feedback, and market insights</p></li><li><p>Support marketing materials development (POSM, product information, presentations)</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>2–5 years of experience in <strong>B2B marketing, trade marketing, or distributor-facing roles</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience working with <strong>distributors or channel partners</strong></p></li><li><p>Background in FMCG, consumer goods, healthcare, industrial, or similar B2B environments preferred</p></li><li><p>Strong coordination and stakeholder management skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with commercial and sales teams</p></li><li><p>Good communication and presentation skills</p></li><li><p>Able to manage multiple projects and timelines<br /><br />email - lucas.chang@swiftsearchglobal.com / whatsapp- 93392324</p><p>EA License No: 18C9495</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lucas Chang<br />EA Personnel No: R1874043</p></li></ul>",
